Date: Fri, 14 Aug 1998 19:05:05 +1000
From: Nobuhiko Okabe <okabenob@crick.nih.go.jp>

In response to previous postings on ProMED-mail, I would like to post
following information from Japan.
Recently, we have released an article on echovirus 30 infections in Japan
entitled "A nationwide epidemic of aseptic meningitis due to echovirus 30
in Japan, 1997-1998" on our publication [IASR: Infectious Agents
Surveillance Reports. This article is also available in English on our web
site <http://idsc.nih.go.jp/iasr/index.html>.
